<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 01:11:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国官员指责俄罗斯和中国阻止亚洲领导人发表声明</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-official-accuses-russia-china-blocking-asia-leaders-statement-2024-10-12/</link><description>一位美国官员表示，他们的反对主要是针对有争议的南海问题上的措辞。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 22:50:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-official-accuses-russia-china-blocking-asia-leaders-statement-2024-10-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国总理在河内同意加强与越南的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-premier-hanoi-agrees-boost-ties-with-vietnam-2024-10-12/</link><description>越南政府表示，越南和中国周六同意加强防务和安全合作，尽管两国在南海存在多年的海上争端。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 17:29:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-premier-hanoi-agrees-boost-ties-with-vietnam-2024-10-12/</guid></item><item><title>台湾中华航空公司表示新飞机订单没有政治压力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/taiwans-china-airlines-says-no-political-pressure-new-aircraft-order-2024-10-12/</link><description>台湾中华航空公司董事长周六表示，在决定是否购买波音或空客飞机以更新其长途机队方面，该公司并未面临任何政治压力。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 11:15:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/taiwans-china-airlines-says-no-political-pressure-new-aircraft-order-2024-10-12/</guid></item><item><title>尽管局势紧张，台湾人仍涌向中国宗教节日</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwanese-flock-china-religious-festival-despite-tensions-2024-10-12/</link><description>本周，一千多名台湾朝圣者涌向中国东南部的福建省参加宗教节日，这是两岸文化交流的罕见实例，但有可能因政治紧张局势而蒙上阴影。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 10:31:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwanese-flock-china-religious-festival-despite-tensions-2024-10-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国警告欧盟不要单独进行电动汽车价格谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-urges-eu-not-affect-ev-tariff-talks-with-separate-price-negotiations-2024-10-12/</link><description>中国周六敦促欧盟不要就中国制造的电动汽车在欧盟销售的价格进行单独谈判，警告称这将“动摇双边关税谈判的基础”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 10:02:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-urges-eu-not-affect-ev-tariff-talks-with-separate-price-negotiations-2024-10-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国谴责总统讲话后威胁采取更多贸易措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-threatens-taiwan-with-more-trade-measures-after-denouncing-presidents-2024-10-12/</link><description>赖清德表示，中华人民共和国无权代表台湾。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 07:53:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-threatens-taiwan-with-more-trade-measures-after-denouncing-presidents-2024-10-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国推出财政刺激措施以重振增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-unveils-fiscal-stimulus-measures-revive-growth-2024-10-12/</link><description>中国财政部周六公布了一项财政刺激计划，旨在重振疲软的经济并实现政府的增长目标，但没有透露新措施的规模。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 06:10:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-unveils-fiscal-stimulus-measures-revive-growth-2024-10-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国的刺激信息让投资者望而却步</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-stimulus-message-leaves-investors-wanting-though-hanging-onto-hope-2024-10-12/</link><description>投资者有充分的理由对北京将花费多少保持谨慎。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 05:51:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-stimulus-message-leaves-investors-wanting-though-hanging-onto-hope-2024-10-12/</guid></item><item><title>投资者对中国经济刺激政策的通报反应冷淡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-investor-reactions-briefing-chinas-finance-ministry-stimulus-2024-10-12/</link><description>中国周六表示，将“大幅增加”政府债务发行，为低收入人群提供补贴、支持房地产市场并补充国有银行资本，以推动重振疲弱的经济增长。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 03:24:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-investor-reactions-briefing-chinas-finance-ministry-stimulus-2024-10-12/</guid></item><item><title>补贴刺激中国汽车销量连续五个月下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-car-sales-rise-snapping-five-month-decline-subsidy-boost-2024-10-12/</link><description>所有收益都来自电池驱动的车辆。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 03:04:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-car-sales-rise-snapping-five-month-decline-subsidy-boost-2024-10-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国提出更多经济财政刺激措施，但未提及规模关键细节</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-will-significantly-increase-debt-revive-economic-growth-2024-10-12/</link><description>新的财政刺激措施一直是金融市场激烈投机的主题。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 02:37:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-will-significantly-increase-debt-revive-economic-growth-2024-10-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国大型银行将于10月25日下调现有抵押贷款利率</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-big-banks-cut-existing-mortgage-rates-oct-25-2024-10-12/</link><description>随着当局加大力度刺激世界第二大经济体，中国四大国有银行周六宣布从 10 月 25 日起下调现有抵押贷款利率。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 02:05:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-big-banks-cut-existing-mortgage-rates-oct-25-2024-10-12/</guid></item><item><title>美国立法者寻求电信公司对中国黑客攻击报告的答复</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-lawmakers-seek-answers-telecoms-chinese-hacking-report-2024-10-11/</link><description>在有报道称中国黑客访问了美国宽带提供商的网络后，美国两党议员小组周五要求 AT&amp;amp;T、Verizon Communications 和 Lumen Technologies 回答问题。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 16:20:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-lawmakers-seek-answers-telecoms-chinese-hacking-report-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国称富士康员工涉嫌受贿、贪污</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-foxconn-employees-probed-bribery-embezzlement-2024-10-11/</link><description>中国政府周五表示，全球最大的 iPhone 组装商台湾富士康的员工因涉嫌受贿和贪污而接受调查，此前台湾方面报道称他们被拘留。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 14:58:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-foxconn-employees-probed-bribery-embezzlement-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国和越南将签署铁路、农业协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-vietnam-set-sign-deals-railway-links-agriculture-sources-say-2024-10-11/</link><description>两位了解相关计划的人士称，中国总理李强本周末访问河内期间，中国和越南预计将签署新协议，包括促进铁路连接和农产品贸易的协议。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 09:45:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-vietnam-set-sign-deals-railway-links-agriculture-sources-say-2024-10-11/</guid></item></channel></rss>